Value: Victory Offices Limited provides workspace services for individuals and businesses in Australia. The company offers space to private serviced, virtual, and day offices; training and board rooms; and co-working, hot desks, and shared and meeting spaces, as well as victory lounge, auditorium, and event spaces. It also offers covid-19 risk solutions, such as virtual assistance and business continuity programs. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Melbourne, Australia. Victory Offices Limited is a subsidiary of Victory Group Holdings Pty Ltd.
